Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.63,0:00:10.94,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,It appeared as though humanity \Nwould be destroyed by the demon.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.54,0:00:17.37,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,But a single mage saved them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.37,0:00:22.30,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,His name was Lumiere Silvamillion Clover.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.51,0:00:31.80,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,He would eventually be called the first \NWizard King, and he became a legend.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.01,0:00:39.82,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,The devil we sealed away 500 years ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.49,0:00:43.52,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,The day his seal would be \Nbroken was drawing near.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.45,0:00:46.31,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Going against all reason in this world,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.73,0:00:49.16,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I somehow assumed the form of a bird
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.16,0:00:52.02,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,and continued to watch over Licht's grimoire.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.07,0:00:57.94,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,This place was now known as Hage Village,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.94,0:00:59.99,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,a place far, far away from the royal capital
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.99,0:01:02.38,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,of the Clover Kingdom, out in the boonies.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.38,0:01:04.58,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,A small village in the Forsaken Realm.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.58,0:01:21.87,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Asta, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.73,0:01:28.43,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so sorry. It's all \Nmy fault... I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.17,0:01:33.05,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,This is nothin'!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.69,0:01:37.91,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna become the Wizard King.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.51,0:01:43.91,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna become the Wizard King... \Nand protect you and everyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.26,0:01:49.13,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna make everyone even happier! \NSo we can have even nicer things!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.42,0:01:52.96,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,And then, I'm gonna prove to everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.15,0:01:55.55,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Prove?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.97,0:02:00.61,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,That even if you're poor... or an orphan...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.55,0:02:04.68,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,you can still become the Wizard King.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.13,0:02:06.29,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,We can?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.70,0:02:08.02,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.49,0:02:11.36,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Can we really?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.36,0:02:16.03,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Anyone can... if they work hard enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.78,0:02:18.70,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Anyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.70,0:02:21.70,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Me, or even you, Yuno!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.47,0:02:31.71,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,I'll... never cry again.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.25,0:02:34.50,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I... no...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.57,0:02:36.71,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Yuno?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.14,0:02:38.15,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,I will...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.82,0:02:40.97,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,I'll become the Wizard King, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.97,0:02:45.75,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,I'll get stronger, and protect \Nyou and everyone else!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.75,0:02:50.02,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna make everyone happier! \NSo we can have nicer things!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.26,0:04:24.61,Ep Title,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Nero Reminisces... \NPart Two
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.18,0:04:31.20,main,Patry,0000,0000,0000,,Where... am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.79,0:04:33.46,main,Patry,0000,0000,0000,,What in the world is going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.90,0:04:36.08,main,Patry,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't I die?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.29,0:04:41.63,main,Patry,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?! Licht?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.13,0:04:45.63,italics,Patry,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on? \NI somehow look like Licht!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.31,0:04:50.14,italics,Patry,0000,0000,0000,,Did my soul somehow end up in Licht?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.79,0:04:53.89,italics,Patry,0000,0000,0000,,No... The feeling of this mana...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.89,0:04:56.18,italics,Patry,0000,0000,0000,,This body... It's human!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.69,0:04:59.15,italics,Patry,0000,0000,0000,,A human that looks like Licht?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.59,0:05:02.90,italics,Patry,0000,0000,0000,,That's right... I'm sure that I died.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.75,0:05:08.60,italics,Patry,0000,0000,0000,,The thing that Licht activated \Nwhen our magic was sealed...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.60,0:05:10.93,italics,Patry,0000,0000,0000,,It must've been forbidden magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.47,0:05:14.06,italics,Patry,0000,0000,0000,,Meaning... a reincarnation spell.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.87,0:05:17.93,main,Patry,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.93,0:05:22.05,italics,Patry,0000,0000,0000,,I can tell... I can feel them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.05,0:05:24.29,italics,Patry,0000,0000,0000,,Raia's soul...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.29,0:05:27.26,italics,Patry,0000,0000,0000,,The souls of all the elves from the village!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.73,0:05:31.35,italics,Patry,0000,0000,0000,,Licht must have activated a reincarnation \Nspell in those last moments!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.89,0:05:34.60,italics,Patry,0000,0000,0000,,In order to save us elves!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.90,0:05:41.93,italics,Patry,0000,0000,0000,,I have...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.57,0:05:44.23,italics,Patry,0000,0000,0000,,been chosen.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.35,0:05:46.49,italics,Patry,0000,0000,0000,,I will become Licht.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.46,0:05:49.16,italics,Patry,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what I have to do...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.74,0:05:52.16,italics,Patry,0000,0000,0000,,I will bring back all the elves.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.07,0:05:54.66,italics,Patry,0000,0000,0000,,And this time...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.66,0:05:59.45,main,Patry,0000,0000,0000,,The humans betrayed someone precious \Nto me. They betrayed all of us!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.45,0:06:00.42,main,Patry,0000,0000,0000,,This time...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.59,0:06:04.18,main,Patry,0000,0000,0000,,This time, we'll destroy the humans!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.70,0:06:14.14,main,Patry,0000,0000,0000,,The only ones I can resurrect \Nright now are these three.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.14,0:06:19.77,main,Patry,0000,0000,0000,,For a complete rebirth... In order \Nto resurrect everyone else,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.77,0:06:23.11,main,Patry,0000,0000,0000,,I will require a phenomenal \Namount of power and sacrifices.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.50,0:06:27.35,main,Patry,0000,0000,0000,,We'll gather the magic stones \Nthat were once in our village,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.35,0:06:31.01,main,Patry,0000,0000,0000,,which have now been scattered.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.82,0:06:33.66,main,Patry,0000,0000,0000,,By using the humans, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.13,0:06:35.59,main,Patry,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that a wonderful idea?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.59,0:06:36.50,main,Raia,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.50,0:06:38.17,main,Fana,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do this, Licht.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.17,0:06:40.49,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,We will get revenge against \Nthose loathsome humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.49,0:06:43.21,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,I will give them endless despair!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.55,0:06:49.51,main,Patry,0000,0000,0000,,Humans, you shall serve as the\Nfoundation of the resurrection.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.51,0:06:59.77,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Resurrecting the elves and getting \Nrevenge on the humans....
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.33,0:07:02.63,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,It was all due to a tragic misunderstanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.46,0:07:05.98,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,But they didn't know any better.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.74,0:07:11.99,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything happened according \Nto how a devil had planned it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.81,0:07:18.50,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,The royal capital... The Clover Kingdom \Nitself was about to be overrun by dark clouds.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.29,0:07:22.78,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,But at that time,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.59,0:07:25.67,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I spotted hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.47,0:07:36.39,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,A gri... moire?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.94,0:07:41.94,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,My prince... Finally...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.62,0:07:44.14,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,The time has come.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.47,0:07:56.74,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,The three leaves of the clover\N represent faith, hope, and love.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.87,0:08:00.91,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Within a fourth leaf dwells good luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.61,0:08:03.83,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Within a fifth leaf...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.63,0:08:07.01,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,resides a devil.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.14,0:08:10.61,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,That devil happened
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.61,0:08:14.25,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,to be different from the one who \Nhad destroyed the elves' village.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.89,0:08:20.10,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,That devil would end up aiding \Nthe boy with no magic, Asta.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.58,0:08:23.64,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Eventually, Patry and his comrades would
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.05,0:08:26.03,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,call themselves the Eye of the Midnight Sun
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.03,0:08:28.40,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,and set out in search of the magic stones.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.11,0:08:31.33,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,By collecting all of the magic stones,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.33,0:08:34.40,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,they could resurrect the rest of the elves.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.40,0:08:36.24,main,Heath,0000,0000,0000,,This is your execution.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.24,0:08:37.74,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,They attacked a village in the boonies...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.62,0:08:43.21,main,Leopold,0000,0000,0000,,Fuegoleon!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.21,0:08:44.41,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,...attacked the royal capital,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.43,0:08:47.54,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,attacked the Underwater Temple,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.54,0:08:48.67,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,and finally,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.29,0:08:52.67,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,they collected all of the magic stones.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.82,0:09:13.32,main,Kid,0000,0000,0000,,M-Marie?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.82,0:09:20.45,main,Rebecca,0000,0000,0000,,Things keep happening one after \Nanother. What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.00,0:09:27.58,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,What the...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.21,0:09:30.55,main,Raia,0000,0000,0000,,Too bad...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.55,0:09:31.59,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,What is?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.59,0:09:34.86,main,Raia,0000,0000,0000,,The era of the humans has come to an end.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.42,0:09:40.10,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,Yuno... Hamon... Klaus...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.27,0:09:45.39,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Do not talk to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.98,0:09:50.66,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,You are not one of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.63,0:09:55.79,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,The resurrection of the \Nother elves was complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.85,0:10:03.41,main,Patlicht,0000,0000,0000,,Begone, humans!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.13,0:10:06.97,main,Patlicht,0000,0000,0000,,Now, the time for revenge has come!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.41,0:10:25.42,top,All,0000,0000,0000,,Those who guide the elves... \NThe Apostles of Sephira!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.95,0:10:27.64,sign_14960_120_The_Apostles_of_,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(968,1)\blur3}The Apostles of Sephira
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.19,0:10:31.27,main,Raia,0000,0000,0000,,By infusing Gravito Stones with magic,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.27,0:10:33.63,main,Raia,0000,0000,0000,,we will open the door to the underworld
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.63,0:10:35.82,main,Raia,0000,0000,0000,,that was sealed under Clover Castle!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.07,0:10:38.95,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,The hell is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.50,0:10:43.16,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,What in the world is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.16,0:10:46.45,main,Baval,0000,0000,0000,,It's a magic space that acts as the \Nborder between this world and the next.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.45,0:10:50.38,main,Baval,0000,0000,0000,,The elves of antiquity entrusted it \Nto the humans in an ancient pact.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.38,0:10:52.38,main,Baval,0000,0000,0000,,It's called the Shadow Palace.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.02,0:10:59.55,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,By setting the final magic \Nstone into the monument,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.55,0:11:03.03,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,the elves' resurrection would \Nbecome permanent,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.03,0:11:06.35,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,and the souls of their human \Nhosts would be destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.37,0:11:12.15,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Asta and the others gathered at the \NShadow Palace for their final battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.15,0:11:15.69,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,But the thing that awaited them was...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.69,0:11:19.70,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,What is this cold, pitch-black magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.38,0:11:26.53,main,Patlicht,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me he's...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.57,0:11:34.74,main,Patlicht,0000,0000,0000,,A devil!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.81,0:11:39.67,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,What in the world is that creature?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.79,0:11:46.18,main,Demon,0000,0000,0000,,Thought it's still incomplete, I haven't\N been in my own body in centuries.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.18,0:11:49.10,main,Demon,0000,0000,0000,,What a wonderful feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.25,0:11:57.19,main,Demon,0000,0000,0000,,Elf that was chosen by a \Nfour-leaf grimoire, I commend you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.19,0:11:59.93,main,Demon,0000,0000,0000,,I praise you from the bottom of my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.93,0:12:04.09,main,Demon,0000,0000,0000,,for everything you've done up to this point, \Nas well as the results you have shown me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.09,0:12:10.54,main,Demon,0000,0000,0000,,And now, I shall have you taste the \Ndepths of despair, like he did back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.95,0:12:13.58,italics,Patlicht,0000,0000,0000,,What... are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.01,0:12:16.29,italics,Patlicht,0000,0000,0000,,What's... going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.59,0:12:23.13,main,Demon,0000,0000,0000,,That day, the one who tricked the \Nhumans into destroying the elves
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.13,0:12:25.01,main,Demon,0000,0000,0000,,was me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.09,0:12:31.01,main,Demon,0000,0000,0000,,And then you lot managed to let me fool \Nyou in the most amusing way, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.01,0:12:33.73,main,Demon,0000,0000,0000,,The revenge went according to plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.48,0:12:41.28,main,Demon,0000,0000,0000,,All of you are fools!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.28,0:12:44.09,main,Demon,0000,0000,0000,,Five centuries ago, they got in my way,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.09,0:12:47.62,main,Demon,0000,0000,0000,,and though I was close, my incarnation failed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.62,0:12:51.70,main,Demon,0000,0000,0000,,You were the next one I set my sights on.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.11,0:12:58.67,main,Demon,0000,0000,0000,,A new sacrifice that was loved by mana,\N still young, and swayed oh so easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.05,0:13:00.88,main,Demon,0000,0000,0000,,Tragedy and a sense of mission...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.88,0:13:04.98,main,Demon,0000,0000,0000,,That was enough for you to \Ndabble in forbidden magic,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.98,0:13:09.39,main,Demon,0000,0000,0000,,which allowed the elves' souls to \Nbe reincarnated in human bodies.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.39,0:13:11.35,main,Patlicht,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.35,0:13:15.49,main,Patlicht,0000,0000,0000,,The one... The one who reincarnated us is Licht!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.49,0:13:21.11,main,Patlicht,0000,0000,0000,,Even if it meant dabbling in forbidden \Nmagic, he gave us our last hope!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.11,0:13:22.61,main,Demon,0000,0000,0000,,Wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.61,0:13:27.61,main,Demon,0000,0000,0000,,Because I was the one \Nwho reincarnated you elves.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.82,0:13:35.06,main,Demon,0000,0000,0000,,Your leader doesn't want \Nthe humans exterminated.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.75,0:13:40.55,main,Demon,0000,0000,0000,,Restoring the elves and that revenge \Nyou longed for... All false goals.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.34,0:13:46.22,main,Demon,0000,0000,0000,,You merely walked down the \Npath I prepared for you,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.22,0:13:48.47,main,Demon,0000,0000,0000,,neatly leading the other fools after you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.98,0:13:52.51,main,Demon,0000,0000,0000,,You truly did a splendid job.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.94,0:13:56.47,main,Demon,0000,0000,0000,,In the end, it led you to a \Nfuture that Licht didn't want,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.94,0:14:04.95,top,Patlicht,0000,0000,0000,,It's a lie... It's a lie... It's a lie...\N It's a lie... It's a lie...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.47,0:14:02.52,main,Demon,0000,0000,0000,,and my incarnation, which finally \Nallowed my soul to return to my body.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.61,0:14:09.21,main,Demon,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed. You were chosen...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.21,0:14:13.70,main,Demon,0000,0000,0000,,as my brilliant, foolish pawn.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.18,0:14:17.62,main,Demon,0000,0000,0000,,Excellent work.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.93,0:14:27.30,main,Demon,0000,0000,0000,,This is just too amusing!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.71,0:14:35.05,main,Demon,0000,0000,0000,,Elves and humans... Your dreams and \Nambitions make the best playthings!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.91,0:14:42.93,main,Demon,0000,0000,0000,,When the owner of a four-leaf grimoire \Nis engulfed in deep despair,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.55,0:14:46.69,main,Demon,0000,0000,0000,,a five-leaf grimoire is born.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.69,0:14:51.01,main,Demon,0000,0000,0000,,At last, I possess both my body \Nand my pitch-black grimoire.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.01,0:14:57.20,main,Demon,0000,0000,0000,,I can rule over the current world as \Na devil with my true form and power!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.55,0:15:01.48,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,But we weren't about to let \Nthat devil have his way.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.48,0:15:05.75,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I spent all this time alone to \Nensure that wouldn't happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.51,0:15:12.35,main,Nero,0000,0000,0000,,Now that your seal has been broken, \Nthat means my seal will also...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.99,0:15:13.97,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Nero?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.97,0:15:18.73,main,Nero,0000,0000,0000,,What a pathetic state you're in. \NIf only my spell was more complete...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.73,0:15:22.25,main,Lumiere,0000,0000,0000,,No, the only reason I was able \Nto return is because of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.25,0:15:23.61,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.61,0:15:27.27,main,Secré,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back, my prince.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.45,0:15:33.03,main,Lumiere,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry I kept you waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.83,0:15:35.94,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,The first Wizard King...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.94,0:15:38.94,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,The legendary statue had life within it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.94,0:15:40.98,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,And you're—Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.98,0:15:46.11,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,N-N-N-N-N-N-N-N-N-Nero, is that you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.26,0:15:57.39,italics,Secré,0000,0000,0000,,Today, we put an end to this long fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.15,0:16:01.10,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, it's not just us.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.10,0:16:04.79,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We have friends that \Nfeel the same way we do.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.94,0:16:07.19,italics,Secré,0000,0000,0000,,Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.53,0:16:09.66,main,Secré,0000,0000,0000,,Win this, Asta!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.45,0:16:15.95,italics,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,This light... I can feel my power welling forth.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.95,0:16:18.34,italics,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Is Asta at his limit?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.66,0:16:23.83,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Asta, I'm gonna leave you \Nbehind if you can't keep up!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.46,0:16:29.62,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Where do you think you're going, Yuno?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.22,0:16:32.83,italics,Devil,0000,0000,0000,,That anti-magic brat \Nis merely letting himself
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.83,0:16:35.59,italics,Devil,0000,0000,0000,,be pulled along, following that \Nwind magic. He's hopeless.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.59,0:16:38.68,italics,Devil,0000,0000,0000,,They're nothing to worry about... hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.68,0:16:40.68,italics,Devil,0000,0000,0000,,Where'd the anti-magic brat go?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.51,0:16:43.48,italics,Devil,0000,0000,0000,,He hid in the shadows of the severed magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.48,0:16:45.94,italics,Devil,0000,0000,0000,,He's in my blind spot, coming from\N a different direction!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.55,0:16:51.48,italics,Devil,0000,0000,0000,,They're pulling each other in and speeding up!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.48,0:16:52.28,main,Devil,0000,0000,0000,,"Sto—"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.68,0:16:55.57,main,Devil,0000,0000,0000,,"Stop."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.57,0:16:56.40,main,Devil,0000,0000,0000,,"Weaken!"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.40,0:16:57.44,main,Devil,0000,0000,0000,,"Go back!"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.08,0:16:58.32,main,Devil,0000,0000,0000,,"Hold back!"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.44,0:16:58.32,main,Devil,0000,0000,0000,,"Stop!"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.79,0:17:04.58,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I reached my... limit?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.58,0:17:05.79,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Asta!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.35,0:17:08.84,main,Devil,0000,0000,0000,,Too bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.80,0:17:13.26,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Mana Zone...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.10,0:17:19.86,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Dark Cloaked Dimension Slash ~ Equinox!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.32,0:17:19.57,sign_27919_273_Equinox,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Equinox
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.20,0:17:42.09,italics,Devil,0000,0000,0000,,Dark magic can interfere with the other world!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.66,0:17:44.27,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,This ki...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.27,0:17:46.96,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,It's... Captain Yami!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.92,0:17:54.84,main,Devil,0000,0000,0000,,You maggots!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.65,0:18:01.31,main,Secré,0000,0000,0000,,Sealing Recovery Magic...\NHeavenly Prison: Faint Omen.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.97,0:18:05.22,italics,Secré,0000,0000,0000,,I've sealed his physical damage.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.22,0:18:08.39,italics,Secré,0000,0000,0000,,Now it's just a question of whether he \Ncan draw out his anti-magic power.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.05,0:18:09.85,main,Secré,0000,0000,0000,,Asta!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.85,0:18:11.06,main,Devil,0000,0000,0000,,Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.06,0:18:12.25,main,Devil,0000,0000,0000,,Perish!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.25,0:18:14.47,main,Devil,0000,0000,0000,,Disappear!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.05,0:18:20.95,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,You go ahead and do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.65,0:18:29.71,main,Devil,0000,0000,0000,,You pieces of trash!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.18,0:18:31.46,main,Secré,0000,0000,0000,,Asta...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.46,0:18:33.13,main,Secré,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to be...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.10,0:18:36.71,main,Secré,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to be the Wizard King, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.69,0:18:39.90,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.47,0:18:48.73,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Right here, right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.27,0:18:54.11,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'll surpass my limits!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.68,0:19:24.53,main,Devil,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.53,0:19:25.48,main,Devil,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.92,0:19:26.14,main,Devil,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.48,0:19:26.76,main,Devil,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.14,0:19:28.00,main,Devil,0000,0000,0000,,This can't be... Impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.00,0:19:31.45,main,Devil,0000,0000,0000,,Inconceivable... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.75,0:19:36.13,main,Asta's Devil,0000,0000,0000,,Hey there, chief.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.50,0:19:37.96,main,Devil,0000,0000,0000,,Who...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.96,0:19:39.44,main,Devil,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.44,0:19:40.80,main,Devil,0000,0000,0000,,Who...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.45,0:19:44.38,main,Asta's devil,0000,0000,0000,,Like you need to know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.38,0:19:46.85,main,Asta's devil,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't matter how \Nstrong or amazing you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.85,0:19:49.78,main,Asta's devil,0000,0000,0000,,You've lost, and you're about to disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.41,0:19:52.92,main,Asta's devil,0000,0000,0000,,See ya, loser.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.87,0:20:03.66,main,Lumiere,0000,0000,0000,,We... won...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.78,0:20:06.15,main,Secré,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.53,0:20:20.53,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,My prince...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.77,0:20:26.95,main,Lumiere,0000,0000,0000,,I guess it's time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.78,0:20:30.91,main,Lumiere,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have the magic to keep \Nthis body together anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.50,0:20:32.62,main,Secré,0000,0000,0000,,My prince...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.62,0:20:35.34,main,Lumiere,0000,0000,0000,,Secré... Though I guess you might be Nero now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.89,0:20:41.46,main,Secré,0000,0000,0000,,Will you watch their futures and \Nideals play out for me, as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.82,0:20:46.42,main,Secré,0000,0000,0000,,Prince Lumiere! I've always...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.42,0:20:48.89,main,Secré,0000,0000,0000,,If you're going, I'll go with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.89,0:20:50.90,main,Lumiere,0000,0000,0000,,I gave everything I had 500 years ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.90,0:20:53.61,main,Lumiere,0000,0000,0000,,and my life was supposed \Nto end back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.15,0:20:57.26,main,Lumiere,0000,0000,0000,,But thanks to you, I was \Nable to protect the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.78,0:20:58.90,main,Lumiere,0000,0000,0000,,That's more than enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.86,0:21:02.86,main,Lumiere,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want you to close \Noff your own potential.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.75,0:21:08.00,main,Lumiere,0000,0000,0000,,I'm looking forward to futures beyond this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.00,0:21:11.83,main,Lumiere,0000,0000,0000,,Both of the Magic Knights, and the \NClover Kingdom you'll defend.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.21,0:21:22.21,main,Secré,0000,0000,0000,,I... The fact that I got to \Nserve you for all this time...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.21,0:21:23.97,main,Secré,0000,0000,0000,,made me very happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.97,0:21:26.18,main,Lumiere,0000,0000,0000,,And I was happy, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.18,0:21:27.66,main,Lumiere,0000,0000,0000,,Five hundred years...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.66,0:21:31.06,main,Lumiere,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you so much for waiting \Nfor me for five hundred years,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.51,0:21:32.47,main,Lumiere,0000,0000,0000,,Secré.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.86,0:21:50.33,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,My prince...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.95,0:21:54.51,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure there are many \Nmore hardships ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.99,0:21:57.54,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm sure we'll be okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.31,0:22:04.05,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I'm not alone anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.77,0:23:42.35,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The Black Bulls return to where \Ntheir hideout once was.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.78,0:23:44.48,main,,0000,0000,0000,,As they try to reconstruct their hideout,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.48,0:23:47.93,main,,0000,0000,0000,,the Black Bulls become drained \Nand collapse, one by one.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.93,0:23:50.41,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What could be happening to them?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.41,0:23:54.00,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time on {\i1}Black Clover{\i0}, Page 125: "Return."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.40,0:23:54.25,sign_34238_338_Page_2_The_Boys_,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(234,1)}Page 125\N\N{\fs18} Return
